Ok Sunday i was coming home from work and the way i go home the road is surrounded by woods. Well i was going pretty fast cus i wanted to go home a.s.a.p cus i been having a sinus headache for like a week now an it wont go away. Well anyways back to the story, I was driving along and i turned off my highbeams and i see this 9-10 foot dark thing walking, now I'm spooked cus im like WTF WAS THAT and it like ran across the road like a bat out of hell, I know this wasnt a bear cus delaware doesnt have bears and it was walking on two feet, so as a quick reaction i did a 360 to check out what it was. Now people here heard stories from the local Injuns that a woods monsters lives in the woods an you should leave it food an it wont bother you, they used to tell the early settlers of Delaware. Now I'm sure you all are like uh a woods monster?, well I'm talking about Bigfoot, now i looked up shit on him after i came home cus I am sure I saw what i saw I'm not crazy. There has been sightings of him/her in the area i was at before. Now since today i go off I am going there to check shit out cus this has got my attention i want to get footage of this thing, its my goal in life, i know it's out there and i know what i saw. Wish me luck, this is a big deal to me.


-Jamez
